9 COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “ ” to H.P. 1222, L.D. 1827, “An Act to Implement
10 the Recommendations of the Right to Know Advisory Committee Concerning Public
11 Records Requests”
12 Amend the bill in section 2 in subsection 4-A in the 5th line (page 1, line 20 in L.D.)
13 by striking out the following: "point at" and inserting the following: 'date on'
14 Amend the bill in section 2 in subsection 4-A in the 5th line (page 1, line 20 in L.D.)
